network.param.modules.inventory

Interface IInventory

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IBean
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Inventory

    public interface IInventory
extends IBean
    An interface represents the Param Catalogue Inventory.

    This interface IInventory will represents sku, price, min qty, max qty.., ICatalogue defines below categories of operations:

    • setSku method for set SKU

    • setCatalogueID method for set catalogueID.

    • setPrice method for set price.

    • setCostPerItem method for set cost per item.

    • setSGST method for set set SGST

    • setCGST method for set set CGST

    • setIGST method for set set IGST

    • setDiscount method for set discount

    • setLocation method for set warehouse location

    • setVolume method for set volume

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Jitendra Kumar Balla, ParamNetwork
